Welcome to "de_goldeneye_temple_rmx_v2"

Map created By "El_Mexicano"

20 slots in each team for a total of 40 slots 

This is the last version of the map "de_goldeneye_temple_rmx_v2", version that i completely renew of the original "goldeneye temple" (N64) ! i started from the first version of the map and i did a lot of modification
i changed the skybox , the textures , and the structure of the buildings :new corridor , new stairs , new rooms and many surprises !!!
